{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhy1ma1ekn40","created":1776694448931,"text":"JVM","note":"源代码文件 -> 字节码文件(编译器) -> 机器码文件(JVM)；\n.java文件，启用javac编译器进程，编译成.class文件；然后，操作系统启用JVM进程，初始化运行环境，包括类加载器、内存空间、垃圾回收线程；\n1.类加载器\n2.运行时数据区\n3.执行引擎："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyoy1vwbaw0","created":1776760257082,"text":"内存模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyoy5dqvq80","created":1776760264691,"text":"堆"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoyb4i3a80","created":1776760277193,"text":"虚拟机栈"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoyh8bgzk0","created":1776760290484,"text":"本地方法栈"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoyvw9zk80","created":1776760322408,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}